  <p>Buses are operated by <a href="https://www.tper.it">TPER</a>. Tickets can be bought on the bus (1.50 &euro; from vending machines, using coins only) or at tobacco shops, e.g. at the train station (1.30 &euro;). The cost for 10 tickets (city pass) is 12.00 &euro;.</p>
